Demoversion of game TESTAMENT v0.9

Author:       INSANITY
Distribution: SIGNUM

Controls:

F1 - Details
F2 - Realtime map
F3 - floor,ceiling

1,2,3,4       - Change weapon
+/- Num.klav. - Window size
m             - Map (esc-exit map)
ESC           - Back to menu
SPACE         - Open door
AMIGA+smer    - Strafing
ALT           - Fire
SHIFT         - Acceleration

Movement is possible to control by mouse,joystick or keyboard

Cheats (only in this demoversion)

ctrl+a        - full ammo
    +w        - weapons
    +i        - invisibility
    +h        - inmortality
    +n        - next level


Minimum hardware is Amiga 1200 2mb RAM.

This demoversion is freeware

